---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="Operation Child Care Case Study | Upfront" description="See how Upfront revolutionized childcare search for military families in Norfolk, Virginia.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-teal hover:text-brand-teal/80 transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        Back to Case Studies
      </a>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
        Operation Child Care
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-gray">
        Revolutionizing Childcare Search for Military Families in Norfolk, Virginia
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Challenge -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-orange uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        The Challenge
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        The Problem
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        Military families in the Norfolk, Virginia region face unique challenges when searching for suitable childcare options. This fragmented system made it difficult for military families to access a comprehensive list of childcare options, leaving them with limited choices and added stress.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Military childcare programs live in a separate database from licensed programs</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Eligibility varies depending on the family's military status</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Private providers accepting military subsidies were not easily searchable</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Solution -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        The Solution
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        A Unified Platform for Military Families
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-8">
        Upfront developed the first platform for military families that included both military and private (licensed) programs in a single location.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Consolidated Data</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Consolidated multiple datasets, including licensing, military, quality program, and direct provider inputs.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Family Search</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Platform included family search, provider portal to input updates, and admin portal to view supply/demand trends.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Smart Results</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Providers displayed on search results depend on user inputs for personalized, relevant matches.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Results -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
          The Results
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
          Rapid Adoption and Growing Demand
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Upfront's new system was quickly adopted by military families, with increasing demand to expand into other regions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">Thousands</div>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-navy font-medium">
            of family searches within three months of launch
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">200+</div>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-navy font-medium">
            provider pages created, creating a digital presence for more than 80% of programs in the area
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner />
</Layout>
